  <abstract>Highlander brochure advertising workshops on integration in public schools. Topics include Army integration, history of segregation, tenure of integrated faculty, and the economics and geography of segregation. The pamphlet outlines a tentative daily schedule and basic information about Highlander. The cost for the nearly month-long program was $150 while the week-long program ran $40.</abstract>
